Backport CVE-2025-69230 (aiohttp log-flood via invalid cookies) for aiohttp 3.8.6.

Upstream PR #11890 (commit 384a173022c9d057110c1418c5c4ff83a321900f) modifies
aiohttp/_cookie_helpers.py to aggregate invalid cookie names per request and
emit a single DEBUG log record instead of one WARNING per invalid cookie.
